{"tha-ap362:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap362:0.2":"Saddasannakavagga ","tha-ap362:0.3":"Pindapatikattheraapadana ","tha-ap362:1.1":"“Tisso namasi sambuddho, ","tha-ap362:1.2":"vihasi vipine tada; ","tha-ap362:1.3":"Tusita hi idhagantva, ","tha-ap362:1.4":"pindapatam adasaham. ","tha-ap362:2.1":"Sambuddhamabhivadetva, ","tha-ap362:2.2":"tissam nama mahayasam; ","tha-ap362:2.3":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap362:2.4":"tusitam agamasaham. ","tha-ap362:3.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap362:3.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap362:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap362:3.4":"pindapatassidam phalam. ","tha-ap362:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap362:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap362:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap362:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pindapatiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap362:6.1":"Pindapatikattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap362:7.1":"Saddasannakavaggo chattimsatimo. ","tha-ap362:8.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap362:9.1":"Saddasanni yavasiko, ","tha-ap362:9.2":"kimsukorandapupphiyo; ","tha-ap362:9.3":"Alambano ambayagu, ","tha-ap362:9.4":"suputi mancadayako; ","tha-ap362:9.5":"Saranam pindapato ca, ","tha-ap362:9.6":"gatha talisameva ca. "}